1600
01:38:31,234 --> 01:38:33,954
♪ Kau tahu apa maksudku ♪

1601
01:38:34,594 --> 01:38:36,187
♪ Dan gayanya ♪

1602
01:38:36,634 --> 01:38:38,910
♪ Sungguh tiada banding ♪

1603
01:38:40,914 --> 01:38:42,792
♪ Mentari pun terbit ♪

1604
01:38:44,514 --> 01:38:49,633
♪ Mentari pun terbit
Dan kubilang asyik ♪

1605
01:38:50,074 --> 01:38:53,590
Kapan pertama kali kau sadari
anakmu terlalu bagus untukmu?

1606
01:38:53,674 --> 01:38:56,473
♪ Mentari, mentari, mentari,
Mentari pun terbit ♪

1607
01:38:56,554 --> 01:38:58,910
♪ Kembali ke US, kembali ke US ♪

1608
01:38:58,994 --> 01:39:01,384
♪ Kembali ke USSR ♪

1609
01:39:03,154 --> 01:39:04,508
